To ensure the normal operation of the application and the quality of service, we need to collect some of your device information for data statistics and analysis, including:\n
- Device identifiers (such as Android ID)\n
- Application version and running status\n
- Device model and system version\n
- LSPosed version\n
- Magisk/KernelSU version, etc.\n
- Network type and operator information\n\n
All data will be encrypted and will not be associated with personal identity. The data is only used for product feature optimization and will not be shared with third parties.
</string>
